Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:54.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Did you come by to see the fireflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:00.89,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:03.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,I heard that it was almost the season for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:10.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,It seems you were a bit too early, time and season-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,Their numbers have dropped too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:14.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.37,natsume,,0,0,0,,Well then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she possessed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,You can see me even though you're a human child?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.03,natsume,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.65,natsume,,0,0,0,,What a careless human child.
