Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.25,natsume,,0,0,0,,Bothering with me, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,Weren't you possessing that person from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:15.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,Possessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.38,natsume,,0,0,0,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,He's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:20.17,natsume,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:23.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,So he can see youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's an old story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,I used to talk a lot to him when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,For a while, we were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:36.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,But one day, he suddenly couldn't see me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,He couldn't see you anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,Can that even happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:48.49,natsume,,0,0,0,,When people become adults, those kinds of powers tend to become weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,So that happens too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,I heard that he would be getting married soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:01.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,so I thought I would at least see his big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:07.89,natsume,,0,0,0,,Well, our relationship was a lot like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,We're not friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.23,natsume,,0,0,0,,Our relationship is that of a master and pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,Try guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:24.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.70,natsume,,0,0,0,,Blond hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.08,natsume,,0,0,0,,I got it! It's pond woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.50,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm a low-level youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,Plus, I didn't have a name in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't tease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a name, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,What about Curly-noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,Come on, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.68,natsume,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd be able to talk to another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,This must be fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'll be in your care until the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,I said, what do you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.65,natsume,,0,0,0,,What do you think about Curly-noodles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.61,natsume,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Nyanko-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,Then how about Curly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,What a dull radiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're going to sleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.13,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,That night, I had a dream where someone was calling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:34.89,natsume,,0,0,0,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.36,natsume,,0,0,0,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,Takashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.74,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.75,natsume,,0,0,0,,Wake up, I have to go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,How about "Kiyo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.89,natsume,,0,0,0,,How about "Kiyo" as your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,Becoming unable to see youkai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,So that can happen too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:32.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, there was a mountain god in this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:36.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,that fell in love with a human woman, and they would rendezvous secretly at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:43.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,During those times, the fireflies from this pond would light the way for them in the pitch-black darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:52.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,To thank them, the mountain god turned the short-lived fireflies into youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:57.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,In their joy, many of them left the pond,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:03.81,natsume,,0,0,0,,and the fireflies here are said to be the descendants of those who stayed behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just a legend, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:23.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:39.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,the one from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:45.15,natsume,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, I think I tripped over something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're a feisty one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,Is there something in this pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:03.62,natsume,,0,0,0,,Not sure. Besides the fireflies, I guess there are carp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.35,natsume,,0,0,0,,That youkai doesn't attack people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.14,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.47,natsume,,0,0,0,,I couldn't ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,I couldn't ask him if he could see youkai too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,Going to see a human who could see them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:36.12,natsume,,0,0,0,,and asking them about their past would just be trouble for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:41.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,That person is called Akifumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,Because he could see youkai,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:54.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,he suffered much from the looks he got from his family and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,He would come here to cry by himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,and I would hide quietly and watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.06,natsume,,0,0,0,,But one day, he came during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.44,natsume,,0,0,0,,In a rush, I tried to hide,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,but something caught onto my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.15,natsume,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,A youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:23.91,natsume,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,Could we talk for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,I, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm interested in humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:39.26,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in youkai, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,He came the next day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,We talked about many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,We talked and talked so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:53.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, we would play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,So this is how it feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,It feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:20.14,natsume,,0,0,0,,But on one day, his eyes could no longer see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't notice even if I touched him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.06,natsume,,0,0,0,,He would come to the pond and I would call for him several times,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.98,natsume,,0,0,0,,yet he couldn't see me even when I stood right in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you'll be unable to see us one day?
