Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:55.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if you'll be unable to see us one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:58.67,natsume,,0,0,0,,That would be terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.01,natsume,,0,0,0,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:06.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that my wish for the longest time?{needs a better edit}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:13.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,I had always, always wished to be free from all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,I thought I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:56.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,He can no longer see Kiyo's fleeting light,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.69,natsume,,0,0,0,,so why does he continue to go to the pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:05.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,I see, so you can see youkai too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.08,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:11.79,natsume,,0,0,0,,A youkai I met recently told me you could once see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:17.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,When I think about it, it was all like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.67,natsume,,0,0,0,,Is it tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:25.64,natsume,,0,0,0,,It was tough on me because I was always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:30.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,But I was able to get along well with one youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,I came to like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.81,natsume,,0,0,0,,but I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:43.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,But one day, I suddenly couldn't see youkai anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.16,natsume,,0,0,0,,And that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:51.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't forget about her, so I didn't get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.04,natsume,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:57.88,natsume,,0,0,0,,But I finally met a girl I could love with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,And she's a very nice person, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,Our wedding ceremony will be held in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.93,natsume,,0,0,0,,I won't come here anymore, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,Akifumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.69,natsume,,0,0,0,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.94,natsume,,0,0,0,,See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:21.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.95,natsume,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:32.83,natsume,,0,0,0,,Kiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,He found someone important to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.04,natsume,,0,0,0,,not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:44.59,natsume,,0,0,0,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,On that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.02,natsume,,0,0,0,,I had a peaceful dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,It was probably Kiyo's memory that flowed into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.40,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.65,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,I can't see you! Please come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.20,natsume,,0,0,0,,Don't leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.28,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hotaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.42,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hotaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.32,natsume,,0,0,0,,Please come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:40.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,Do you hate me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:47.63,natsume,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.72,natsume,,0,0,0,,Love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:58.52,natsume,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.06,natsume,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.09,natsume,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.51,natsume,,0,0,0,,not Akifumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.22,natsume,,0,0,0,,That's what you were called, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,I saw and heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,I am a firefly youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.19,natsume,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to keep it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,but I'm able to return to being a simple bug just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:56.82,natsume,,0,0,0,,Then you won't be able to keep your current form,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:59.99,natsume,,0,0,0,,and your life will end as a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,Or so I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.66,natsume,,0,0,0,,Even so, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.46,natsume,,0,0,0,,Even without me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:12.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,He will continue to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Then, at the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,even as a bug,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.77,natsume,,0,0,0,,I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.85,natsume,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.27,natsume,,0,0,0,,Wai-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.90,natsume,,0,0,0,,I hope she's not intending to head towards the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:39.53,natsume,,0,0,0,,That huge, big-mouthed guy doesn't attack humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.24,natsume,,0,0,0,,but he eats fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:43.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,Because he's going around and eating them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:47.33,natsume,,0,0,0,,all the fireflies here are hiding somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.71,natsume,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Hotaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's too dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,How irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.60,natsume,,0,0,0,,Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.57,natsume,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:26.00,natsume,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,Where's Hotaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.55,natsume,,0,0,0,,She ran away after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:40.39,natsume,,0,0,0,,This smell... it's someone else's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.80,natsume,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:51.48,natsume,,0,0,0,,My mom got really mad then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.31,natsume,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.87,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's pretty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:05.54,natsume,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.04,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.08,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:15.05,natsume,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.29,natsume,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:20:02.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Did everything go well for the mountain god and his lover that the fireflies protected?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.84,natsume,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:07.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Unlike youkai, humans have a short lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.56,natsume,,0,0,0,,Hotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:14.69,natsume,,0,0,0,,Will the day come when I can't see them either?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:19.65,natsume,,0,0,0,,These one-sided encounters and these troubling days...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.57,natsume,,0,0,0,,Will it be liberating for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.45,natsume,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.21,natsume,,0,0,0,,At that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:38.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,I felt that the small firefly whispered something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:39.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand the bug's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Hotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.43,natsume,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he understood them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.02,natsume,,0,0,0,,Maybe only he could...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:16.37,natsume,,0,0,0,,It's tough when you can't do anything, even though you can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:18.04,natsume,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,You don't have any obligation to help out everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:25.30,natsume,,0,0,0,,In the end, youkai and humans are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.18,natsume,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.97,natsume,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you this, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:35.73,natsume,,0,0,0,,Even if you couldn't see us anymore, I wouldn't let you get away until you give me the Book of Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:41.15,natsume,,0,0,0,,Even if the youkai before me disappear one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:46.49,natsume,,0,0,0,,the memories from my encounters with them will never disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:55.41,natsume,,0,0,0,,Then how about you make an effort to be my bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.58,natsume,,0,0,0,,You promised, right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.92,natsume,,0,0,0,,And they will never go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.34,natsume,,0,0,0,,Not a single one.
